reviewText: Love the old Bette Davis Classics dvd plays well and meets expectations.  The dvd plays well and you can read the plot on wiki if you want to learn more.
Like the Story of Temple Drake, this movie is a bad copy of the original.  Listed as "new" I bought it and am sorry, even the art work was poor.  Never from this seller again.
This is one of the first movies that Bette made. I enjoyed watching it. Her sister steals her boyfriend away from her.
